---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import CTABlock from '../components/CTABlock.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About Field Service Stack"
  description="Independent software reviews and gear recommendations for field service professionals. Built by someone who has worked in the field."
>
  <section class="py-10 md:py-14">
    <div class="max-w-[65ch]">
      <h1 class="mb-6">About Field Service Stack</h1>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          Field Service Stack exists because most software review sites are paid placements dressed up as editorial. The top result is usually whoever writes the biggest check, not whoever builds the best product. That is useless if you are trying to run a real business.
        </p>

        <p>
          This site is different. Every review is based on actual usage. Every comparison uses the same evaluation criteria. Every recommendation accounts for what field service businesses actually need: reliable scheduling, fast invoicing, a mobile app that works on a cell tower in the middle of nowhere, and a price that does not require a second mortgage.
        </p>

        <h2>Who Writes This</h2>

        <p>
          My name is Patrick Gibbs. I have spent years working in field service, specifically sewer and infrastructure inspection across the Southeast. I know what it is like to manage jobs from a truck, deal with scheduling chaos, and wonder why the office software costs more than the equipment.
        </p>

        <p>
          That experience informs everything on this site. When I review a mobile app, I am thinking about whether it works on a job site with one bar of signal. When I evaluate pricing, I am thinking about a three-person crew, not an enterprise with 200 technicians and a CTO.
        </p>

        <h2>Epiphany Dynamics</h2>

        <p>
          Field Service Stack is maintained by <a href="https://epiphanydynamics.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Epiphany Dynamics</a>, an AI automation agency helping service businesses work smarter. We build custom automation workflows, AI-powered scheduling, intelligent dispatch, and whatever else a field service company needs to stop wasting time on manual processes.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you are reading reviews here and thinking "I wish someone would just set all this up for me," that is exactly what we do.
        </p>

        <p>
          <a href="https://epiphanydynamics.ai/book" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            Book a free 30-minute consultation
          </a> and we will walk through your current workflow, identify the biggest time sinks, and recommend the right tools and automations for your business.
        </p>

        <h2>Editorial Policy</h2>

        <ul>
          <li>We do not accept payment for reviews or rankings.</li>
          <li>Some gear pages include affiliate links. These are clearly marked and do not influence scores or recommendations.</li>
          <li>Software vendors do not get to preview or approve content before publication.</li>
          <li>If we get something wrong, we correct it publicly with a note explaining the change.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Contact</h2>

        <p>
          Got a question, tip, or a product you think we should review? Reach out at
          <a href="mailto:patrick@epiphanydynamics.ai">patrick@epiphanydynamics.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <CTABlock />
  </section>
</Base>
